reviewText: Blood Frenzy is one of those movies that is hard to find, ive seen it available couple times and its not a movie that youll find in a video store ether. I recommend this to horror fans!!

Largely a paint by numbers 80's slasher with a twist you'll see coming a mile away, the desert setting and slightly off-center premise of the characters- in which all start out with admitted mental problems- is enough to make it worth one sitting.
